OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781657292
OL,3,CInvest in transport to help Ireland
OL,4,Cwithstand global fuel shocks, says
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,FIreland needs to accelerate investment
OL,8,Fin public transport and EVs to reduce
OL,9,Fits emissions and its exposure to
OL,10,Ffossil fuel shocks, the Climate Change
OL,11,FAdvisory Council has said.
OL,13,FThe independent climate advisory body
OL,14,Falso said that the Government's
OL,15,Femergency measures for fuel price
OL,16,Fincreases were not "sufficiently
OL,17,Ftargeted", and welcomed the incentive
OL,18,Ffor the purchase of new electric
OL,19,Fvehicles.
OL,26,@xD@TOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
