PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781657292
OL,3,CInvest in transport to help Ireland
OL,4,Cwithstand global fuel shocks, says
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,FFuel protests took place in April over
OL,8,Frising prices, which saw cities,
OL,9,Fstreets and motorways across Ireland
OL,10,Fclogged up and blockades of Ireland's
OL,11,Fonly oil refinery in Co Cork.
OL,13,FThis prompted some panic buying at
OL,14,Fforecourts, hundreds of which ran dry,
OL,15,Fand after blockades were lifted in
OL,16,FDublin in a late-night policing
OL,17,Foperation almost a week after they
OL,18,Fbegan, the government unveiled half a
OL,19,Fmillion euro worth of measures to help
OL,20,Fwith the rising cost of fuel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781657292
OL,3,CInvest in transport to help Ireland
OL,4,Cwithstand global fuel shocks, says
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,FThe measures included a reduction in
OL,8,Fexcise duty on petrol, diesel and
OL,9,Fgreen diesel until the end of July,
OL,10,Fand further reducing minimum oil taxes
OL,11,Fby 10 cent per lire on petrol 10 cent
OL,12,Fper litre on diesel, and 2.4 cent per
OL,13,Flitre on green diesel.
OL,15,F"Fossil fuel shocks are not one-off
OL,16,Fevents," said chairperson of the
OL,17,FClimate Change Advisory Council Alex
OL,18,FWhite.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781657292
OL,3,CInvest in transport to help Ireland
OL,4,Cwithstand global fuel shocks, says
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,F"As long as Ireland remains heavily
OL,8,Fdependent on petrol and diesel for
OL,9,Ftransport, people, businesses and
OL,10,Fpublic services will remain exposed to
OL,11,Fglobal price volatility and
OL,12,Fgeopolitical crises.
OL,14,F"The way to reduce that exposure is to
OL,15,Fgive people real alternatives.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781657292
OL,3,CInvest in transport to help Ireland
OL,4,Cwithstand global fuel shocks, says
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,F"That means sustained investment in
OL,8,Fpublic transport, a charging network
OL,9,Fpeople can rely on, and the grid
OL,10,Fcapacity needed to support the switch
OL,11,Fto electric across cars, buses and
OL,12,Fcommercial fleets.
OL,14,F"This transition also has to be fair.
OL,15,FSupports should be targeted at those
OL,16,Fmost exposed to transport fuel costs,
OL,17,Fparticularly people on lower incomes
OL,18,Fand those who are car-dependent
OL,19,Fbecause they do not have access to
OL,20,Fpractical alternatives.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781657292
OL,3,CInvest in transport to help Ireland
OL,4,Cwithstand global fuel shocks, says
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,F"The Government has set the right
OL,8,Fambition to end Ireland's reliance on
OL,9,Ffossil fuels, the test now is
OL,10,Fdelivery."
OL,12,FThe Council also warned that Ireland's
OL,13,Ftransport network must be made more
OL,14,Fresilient to extreme weather.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781657292
OL,3,CInvest in transport to help Ireland
OL,4,Cwithstand global fuel shocks, says
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,FIt said Storm Chandra and prolonged
OL,8,Frainfall in early 2026 exposed the
OL,9,Fvulnerability of road and rail
OL,10,Finfrastructure, underlining the need
OL,11,Ffor climate risk to be built into
OL,12,Ftransport planning, investment and
OL,13,Fdesign standards.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781657292
OL,3,CInvest in transport to help Ireland
OL,4,Cwithstand global fuel shocks, says
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,FThe council is also calling for the
OL,8,Fupdated National Ports Policy to be
OL,9,Ffinalised and published, for greater
OL,10,Finvestment in climate-resilient
OL,11,Fregional and local roads, and for
OL,12,Fvulnerable sections of the rail
OL,13,Fnetwork to be assessed and climate-
OL,14,Fproofed.
OL,16,FIt also called for targeted measures
OL,17,Fto increase EV uptake among lower-
OL,18,Fincome households, particularly in
OL,19,Fareas with limited access to public
OL,20,Ftransport and high car dependency.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781657292
OL,3,CInvest in transport to help Ireland
OL,4,Cwithstand global fuel shocks, says
OL,5,Ccouncil
OL,7,FThe acceleration of the expansion of
OL,8,FEV charging infrastructure, including
OL,9,Fthe real time mapping of EV charging
OL,10,Fpoints to give people and businesses
OL,11,Fconfidence in the alternatives to
OL,12,Ffossil fuel use, was also recommended.
OL,14,FPublicly accessible charging
OL,15,Finfrastructure in Ireland remains well
OL,16,Fbelow the EU average.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
